

combine

 - 325 g 110F water
 - 1 tbsp brown sugar

add

 - 2.5 g instant yeast

rest 5 minutes
combine in stand mixer bowl

 - 500 g ap flour
 - 10 g salt

add liquid
combine
knead on 3 for 5 minutes
knead on 2 for 5 minutes

rest 60-90 minutes at 24C until doubled

meanwhile bring to boil

 - 1 liters water
 - 1/4 cup baking soda

set oven to 450
line baking sheets with parchemin

oil surface and top of dough
flatten dough
shape into a rectangle
split dough in 12 rectangles
roll into 12 inches rope
rest covered 10 minutes 
roll to 20-22 inches rope
form into pretzel: https://youtu.be/3qZZRSYc5FU?t=130

rest 15 minutes
boil for 30 seconds upside down
sprinkle with salt

bake 20 minutes until golden

----
replace half water with milk or pilsner beer
use up to 3 tbsp butter
hydration from other recipes 55-75%
increase temperature to 450
